$PROB MELPHALAN-OSU11055 TWO COMPARTMENT INFUSION PKPD $INPUT NOTE ID TIME ANC DV AMT RATE MDV DVID CMT WT BSA SEX AGE CRCL FFM HCT P53FOLD IC50 SLC7A5 $DATA ..\PKPD_OSU11055_Neutropenia_lnplus4.csv IGNORE=#
$SUBR ADVAN6 TOL=3
$MODEL COMP=(PKCENTR) COMP=(PKPERI) COMP=(STEM) COMP=(ANC,DEFOBS) COMP=(TRANSIT1) COMP=(TRANSIT2) COMP=(TRANSIT3) COMP=(INPUT2)
$PK
TVCL=THETA(1)*((CRCL/91.94)**THETA(14))*((FFM/59.90)**(0.75))*((HCT/32.50)**THETA(16)) TVV1=THETA(2)*(FFM/59.90) TVQ=THETA(3)*((FFM/59.90)**(0.75)) TVV2=THETA(4)*(1+SLC7A5*THETA(15))*(FFM/59.90)
CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1)) V1=TVV1*EXP(ETA(2)) Q=TVQ*EXP(ETA(3)) V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(1)*THETA(5))
S1=V1
K10=CL/V1 K12=Q/V1 K21=Q/V2
BASE=THETA(6)*EXP(ETA(4)) MTT=THETA(7)*EXP(ETA(5)) K=4/MTT POWER1=THETA(8) SLOPE=THETA(9)*EXP(ETA(6)) KE=LOG(2)/THETA(10)
IPT=THETA(11)*EXP(ETA(7))
IP0=THETA(12)*EXP(ETA(8))
A_0(3)=KE*BASE/K A_0(4)=BASE A_0(5)=KE*BASE/K A_0(6)=KE*BASE/K A_0(7)=KE*BASE/K A_0(8)=IP0
$DES CP=A(1)/V1 DRUG=SLOPE*CP ;****************KINETICS**************************** DADT(1)=A(2)*K21-A(1)*K10-A(1)*K12 DADT(2)=A(1)*K12-A(2)*K21 ;****************DYNAMICS****************************
FN=(BASE/0.001)**POWER1 IF(A(4).GT.0.001) FN=(BASE/A(4))**POWER1 KIN=0 IF(TIME.GT.72) KIN=1/IPT
DADT(3)=K*A(3)*(1-DRUG)*FN - K*A(3) ;STEM DADT(4)=K*A(7) - KE*A(4) + KIN*A(8) ;ANC DADT(5)=K*A(3) - K*A(5) ;TRANSIT 1 DADT(6)=K*A(5) - K*A(6) ;TRANSIT 2 DADT(7)=K*A(6) - K*A(7) ;TRANSIT 3 DADT(8)=-KIN*A(8) ; INPUT2
$ERROR IPRED=F IF (CMT .EQ. 4) IPRED=LOG(F)+4 IRES=DV-IPRED W=THETA(13) IF(W.EQ.0) W=1 IWRES=IRES/W
QK=0 QD=0 IF (CMT .EQ. 1) QK=1 IF (CMT .EQ. 4) QD=1
PKY=IPRED * EXP(ERR(1)) PDY=IPRED + W*ERR(2)
Y=QK*PKY+QD*PDY
$THETA 29.3 FIX ; THETA1 19.6 FIX ; THETA2 28.3 FIX ; THETA3 20.8 FIX ; THETA4 1.31 FIX; THETA5 5.2 FIX ;THETA6 105 FIX ;THETA7 0.209 FIX ;THETA8 10.3 FIX ;THETA9 7 FIX ; THETA10 12.9 FIX; THETA11 19.9 FIX; THETA12 0.624 FIX ; THETA13
0.148 FIX; THETA14 -0.116 FIX; THETA15 0.205 FIX; THETA16
$OMEGA 0.0777 FIX ;ETA1 0.0681 FIX ;ETA2 0.287 FIX ;ETA3 0.111 FIX ;ETA4 0.00987 FIX ;ETA5 0.0778 FIX ;ETA6 0 FIX ; ETA7 2.39 FIX; ETA8
$SIGMA 0.0588 FIX ; EPS1 1 FIX ;EPS2
$SIMULATION (9215690) ONLYSIM SUBPROBLEMS=200
$TABLE ID TIME AMT MDV DVID CMT Y IPRED ONEHEADER NOPRINT FILE=119pt_pkpd_neutropenia_inputdelay_sim100.fit
